ActCanada Customs and Revenue Agency Act
PrecisAppointment of HOWARD A. LEESON of Regina, Saskatchewan, selected from a list of nominees submitted by the Province of Saskatchewan, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Customs and Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
